      <title>在特朗普申请批评之后</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-01/ukraine-pushing-ahead-on-us-deal-after-trump-renews-criticism</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乌克兰的顶级外交官说，在唐纳德·特朗普总统指责基夫试图重新谈判这笔交易的几个小时后，官员们向美国敦促向美国迈向“可接受的”经济协议。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-01/ukraine-pushing-ahead-on-us-deal-after-trump-renews-criticism</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 01 Apr 2025 08:50:22 GMT</pubDate>
